    "title": "Vacancy for Hotel Manager at Compass Group India Digital Technologies",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Hotel Manager with drive and ambition, Compass Group India Digital Technologies in Bengaluru is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Compass Group India Digital Technologies:\nCompass Group India Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bengaluru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Compass Group India Digital Technologies!",
